Package Description
VersaoConcorrente
Package with all sub-packages. 1 - Package Apoio: contains the FIFO 2 - Atores Principais: contains the actors: Ordinary Thief and Master Thief 3 - Parametros do Problema: Contains all the constants and the General Repository 4 - Regioes: Divided in Concentration Site; Collection Site; Assault Partys and Museum
VersaoConcorrente.Apoio
Contains the structure associated to the FIFO.
VersaoConcorrente.AtoresPrincipais
Package that contains the Actors - Normal Thief - Master Thief
VersaoConcorrente.ParametrosDoProblema
Package with all the constants used in this problem.
